title: Dance Moms S04E19 The Battle of Maddie vs Chloe WEB-DL x264-RKST
description:
Episode: 19
The Battle of Maddie vs. Chloe
Original Airdate: May 13, 2014 The rivalry between Maddie and Chloe has boiled for four seasons and this episode of Dance Moms traces the very beginnings of it. Maddie and Chloe battled for first place in competitions, first position on the pyramid and ultimately, for a place in Abby's heart... But is the rivalry really between them...or between their mothers?
